---
title: Sweet Soy Chicken Cutlets with a Roasted Sweet Potato & Pepper Jumble
description: Raise your hand if the biggest question of your week is always, “What the heck am I eating for dinner?!” We’re right there with you. But we’ve got you covered: The answer to that question is pretty delicious. We’re serving up succulent chicken cutlets with a side of roasted sweet potatoes, bell pepper, and poblano all tossed in garlicky lime butter. To finish things off, the chicken is drizzled with a ridiculously delicious soy-spiked pan sauce. Talk about a dream come true!
